@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qxmuda(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v2 + 0.93)) / wp.exp(wp.cos(v0 + 1.00)))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.sin(wp.sin(v1 + 0.68)))
    tmp = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.58 - v0 + 0.33)) + ((v2 + 0.84 * v1 + 0.06) - wp.cos(v2 + 0.92)))
    v2 = 0.33
    v1 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.98 / tmp + 0.53)) + v1)
    data[tid] = v0
